1:1 COMMENT "# io_protocol_closer.z -- project a file value to `closer` and pass"
1:68 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "# it through a protocol-typed parameter."
2:41 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "#"
3:2 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# Exercises the vtable machinery: `io.file` declares `:closer`"
4:63 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# conformance, and `fr.closer` projects the file value to a"
5:60 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# `closer` handle (borrowed; does not move ownership). The `tidy`"
6:66 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "# function receives that handle and invokes `close` via the vtable \u{2014}"
7:69 EOL "\n"
8:1 COMMENT "# same method that direct dispatch on `fr.close` would call, but"
8:65 EOL "\n"
9:1 COMMENT "# reached through a protocol boundary."
9:39 EOL "\n"
10:1 EOL "\n"
